bilingual.target: 我们需要填满这个表格。

bilingual.source: Fill the shaker with ice before adding the liquids.
bilingual.target: 在加入液体之前，先用冰块填满调酒器。

bilingual.source: I like to fill my pita with hummus and vegetables.
bilingual.target: 我喜欢用鹰嘴豆泥和蔬菜填满我的皮塔饼。

bilingual.source: The crew is pumping water into the pool to fill it up.
bilingual.target: 工作人员正在往泳池里抽水填满它。

bilingual.source: You can use any type of infilling to fill this gap.
bilingual.target: 你可以用任何类型的填充物来填满这个空隙。

bilingual.source: We need to buy a piece of furniture to fill this empty room.
bilingual.target: 我们需要买一件家具来填满这个空房间。

bilingual.source: I like to fill my pitta with fresh vegetables and hummus.
bilingual.target: 我喜欢用新鲜蔬菜和鹰嘴豆泥填满我的皮塔饼。

bilingual.source: Be sure to fill the lined space completely.
bilingual.target: 请务必完全填满横线里的空间。

bilingual.source: We feel a pressure to fill these different-sized bottles as they pass.
bilingual.target: 当这些不同大小的瓶子经过时，我们对要填满它们感到有一种压力。

list.abstract: Fill（英[fɪl]，美[fɪl]），英语单词。可以用作动词，名词，做名词时，指最大需求量，最大容量，填料；做动词时，指使充满，装满，注满。英语短语有fill in the form ，译为填表。例句：Fill one large bucket with water.（在一个大桶里装满水。） 复数：fills ，第三人称单数： fills ，现在分词： filling ，过去式： filled， 过去分词： filled。
Fill即Fill() 函数。是MATLAB、C++中的fill函数。

yingyinNormal.en: They'll fill the pits, they'll crawl over one another.
yingyinNormal.zh: 它们会填满坑，一个叠一个。

yingyinNormal.en: Is it going to take long? It'll take as long as it'll take. We have to make a hole. We fill it in and the road is mended.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是不是需要很长时间？需要多少时间要看具体的情况了。我们得先要挖个坑。再用沙子填满。然后呢，道路就修好了。

yingyinNormal.en: I had to fill the post.
yingyinNormal.zh: 总要有人担任那个职位。

yingyinNormal.en: We still need to fill Jacobs' seat.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们还得找人接替雅各布斯呢。

yingyinNormal.en: Hold on. Fill these out. Sit over there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等等，拿去填资料，坐在那儿填。

yingyinNormal.en: There are a couple of forms to fill out. Easy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 要填几份表格。简单。

yingyinNormal.en: Why don't you fill out this address card? Oh, okay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 麻烦你填一下住址。好的。

yingyinNormal.en: Look around you. Have you not had your fill of death?
yingyinNormal.zh: 看看你们周围死的人，还不够多吗？
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《The Hobbit: The Battle of the Five Armies》

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, look, I do something nice, okay? I'll fill her ice trays.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我会做一些好事，我会帮她把制冰盒加水，好吗？

yingyinNormal.en: But I'm not in love with her as I am with you. You fill my brain.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但我对她的爱不及对你这般强烈，我满脑子想的都是你。

yingyinNormal.en: Trouble sleeping? I slept for 70 years, sir. I think I've had my fill.
yingyinNormal.zh: 睡不着了？一觉睡了70年 长官 我觉得睡够了。

yingyinNormal.en: Look around. You're in a bowl. Bowl's gonna fill up. Ain't no way out.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们看看，你们等于住在碗里，碗一装满水就无处可逃罗。

yingyinNormal.en: My name is Galgo. Let me fill you in. l am good. Very good. At warfare.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的名字叫，高格，我跟你介绍一下，我很棒，打起仗来，非常棒。

yingyinNormal.en: Would you like some wine? Yeah, fill her up. I'll tell you when to stop.
yingyinNormal.zh: 想来点红酒吗？好，给我倒上，叫你停再停。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I'm gonna fill in for him as food critic for the Chelsea Reporter.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要替他代班，帮切尔西报道（没什么人看的地区性小报纸）做美食评鉴。

yingyinNormal.en: I can't believe you have to fill out a preschool application for an infant.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我真不敢相信你得为一个婴儿开始填幼儿园的申请表。

yingyinNormal.en: I think I've had my fill of new. You think I'm a child of Ultron? You're not?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的确是新生的，你们以为我是奥创的继任者？你不是吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, darn it, we're all out of milk. Hey, Chandler, would you fill me up here?
yingyinNormal.zh: 该死，没牛奶了，钱德，能不能给我加一点？

yingyinNormal.en: I see what you guys are saying. I'll go downstairs and fill out an application.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，我懂了，我下楼填申请表。

yingyinNormal.en: Wow. Cool house. I know, right? Just a few thing I stole to help fill the void.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哇哦，房子超酷。不错吧？就是偷了几样东西，填填空荡荡的家。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Jeremy Wright, the culture secretary, should welcome this positive, hope-<highlight>filled</highlight> proposal, and tum it into action.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 英国文化部大臣Jeremy Wright应该欣然接受这一积极的、充满希望的提议，并将其转化为行动。

examination_example.sentence: But it doesn't necessarily follow from findings like these that a world without work would be <highlight>filled</highlight> with unease.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但这些发现并不一定意味着一个没有工作的世界会充满不安。

examination_example.sentence: Mine is <highlight>filled</highlight> with leftovers, bread, stock, meat and fish.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我的满是剩菜、面包、牲畜、肉和鱼。

examination_example.sentence: As a result, farms have grown increasingly reliant on temporary guest workers using the H-2A visa to <highlight>fill</highlight> the gaps in the workforce.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 因此，农场越来越依赖使用H-2A签证的临时外来工人来填补劳动力缺口。

examination_example.sentence: Koziatek's Manchester School of Technology High School is trying to <highlight>fill</highlight> that gap.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 科齐亚特克的曼彻斯特理工高中正试图填补这一空白。

examination_example.sentence: There're enough people to <highlight>fill</highlight> the jobs at McDonalds and other places where you don't need to have much skill.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在麦当劳和其他不需要太多技能的地方，有足够的人来填补职位空缺。

word_usage.usage:
be filled with和be full of同义，可以互相转化，注意fill是动词，full是形容词。
如：The bottle was filled with water.=The bottle was full of water.
那个瓶子里装满了水。
